Jerron saw her.  He had felt her mind, screaming in pain from the bathroom.  She had taken the pills.  More than usual this time, her mind, it practically shut down.  A small amount of sympathy crept into his mind as he thought how shitty she must feel, but then he remembered it was she that chose to do this to herself.  They ALL chose to do this to themselves.  I could heal them all, I know how.  The mind is limitless, but only to those who know how to break the limits.  In his usual eerie quiet voice, he spoke, &quot;Idiots.&quot;  He rose to his feet walking over to near Nefi, who had emerged from the bathroom a few shades paller than before, but what intrigued him was her mind.  It showed not the usual dulling effects of the pills.  The drugs yes, but the pills she had taken moments earlier...no.  Odd.  The screams, they stopped, but not from the pills.  As he walked by, he caressed her cheek with his hand.  He spoke to her, only to her, &quot;meet with me, come to my home, I have need to speak with you.&quot;  Giving her not but a chance to wonder, he walked out of the room, lifting his clouds of misery from them all. <p>Ignis Summa Pugnabat, The fires shall cleanse the world.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/usuedydar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Suedydar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Knight of Souls</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/4/02 1:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: S'just Life.</span><hr size=1>   What was that? Jash has returned from his business and sat back on the couch. As Jerron walked out of the room he peered at him, pondering what he said. &quot;Might be better not to know...not really any of my business any way..&quot; thought Jash to himself. He busied himself with a new psychic game HardTec. had invented.<br>
  Concentrating on the orb he held in his hand Jash slipped into a world all his own. Anything he desired could come true..anything. Right now he just wanted to skate with no interruptions. Instantly a giant skate park appeared before him. Summoning his board he began to hover a few inches off the air. Go time. (ooc: I'll leave all the fancy tricks and grinds up to you to imagine, can't remember everything off TH2 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
