<br>
Untangling her legs, she let them hang into the grafitti covered bowl. She leaned forward and gripped the edge where the flats met the top of the bowl, her violet eyes caught sight of a tall lanky boy wipe out. Laughter filled her and sparkled in her smile and eyes, &quot;Hey! Skeet!&quot;<br>
<br>
The laughter began to roll off her tongue and out of her mouth, as she waited for him to give her his attention from the bottom of the bowl. Once he looked, she grabbed her hover board and jumped on, &quot;Let me show you how it's done.&quot;<br>
<br>
