&quot;... ok.. yeah blood is hard to get outta stuff.....er...  hehe&quot; devin smiled hoping not to freak anyone out as his ears went back in a embrassed look.<br>
<br>
  derek parked at the cyberia<br>
&quot;......  i hope no one asks me to dance&quot; devin said shifting his stance a little as he got out<br>
<br>
&quot; why you cant?&quot;  mika said looking around<br>
<br>
&quot; not at all the term bear in sandles comes to mind when i even try,  i can only slow dance if even that......&quot; devin mumbled off again he had a tendency to talk to much he trys to not .<br>
<br>
 he walked in first and looked around at the blaring tencho music &quot;..... yay tencho!&quot; devin smiled&quot; ok i'll go   look around a bit. i wonder if  kali's still here&quot; devin smiled as his ears perked up as his tail wen into a question mark  like pose.<br>
<br>
&quot; have fun bondage kitty!&quot;   jash shouted as devin turned around<br>
&quot; YOU  BASTARD GET BACK HERE!!!&quot; devin chased after him for a while.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot; oh @#%$! DEVIN!!!&quot; derek yelled as devin walked back<br>
<br>
&quot; sorry...&quot; devin looked down as his claws  as they sheathed.<br>
<br>
&quot; no killing people!&quot; mika said then  fake scolded devin as they both cracked up.<br>
<br>
&quot; i wouldnt kill anyone in plain view! i may be insane but im not stupid&quot; devin laughed&quot; well im gonna go find kali seeya luv ya all!' he waved at  the group then walked off to find this person he called kali.<br>
<br>
 the tencho music blared  out as he saw kali.<br>
&quot; HEY!&quot; devin called out as  kali turned around. she had almost platnium colored hair and red eyes.( yes  a her)<br>
 she wore  a long violet coat covering  everything but her feet  which she wore <br>
 she smiled and hugged him<br>
&quot; hey pretty kitty&quot; she kissed him on the cheek<br>
&quot;.......  you know i dont like that name?&quot; devin smiled as they walked to a  table.<br>
&quot; but  its so cute, jus like you? hey your eyes keep on changing color......&quot; kali said as they sat down<br>
<br>
&quot; oh......crap&quot; devin said as kali kissed him.<br>
&quot;   you been stayin away from shrooms like i told ya pretty kitty?&quot;<br>
&quot; since when do i do anything ya tell me too?&quot; devin said<br>
<br>
&quot;  what! you just stopped refering to me as the domantrix!&quot; kali laughed<br>
<br>
 devin looks at two  guys staring at him.<br>
<br>
( wow that  cat-guy is cute)<br>
<br>
( hey i think hes straight look at that chick)<br>
<br>
( oh yeah.. oh crap)<br>
<br>
( im bi acutally..but in a realtionship,sowy)<br>
<br>
( AH did he just talk in our minds!?)<br>
( scary.....)<br>
<br>
( @#%$ off)<br>
<br>
 they both walked away<br>
<br>
&quot; devin!?&quot; kali said<br>
<br>
&quot; what!&quot;  devin said attempting to look innocent<br>
<br>
&quot; oh c'mon dont try that crap with me, i've known you forever man&quot; kali kissed him again and put him on her lap.<br>
&quot; theres my lap cat&quot; she smiled<br>
&quot;.... do you think i should be embrassed&quot; devin asked and made a purring like noise<br>
<br>
&quot; maybe.....&quot; she said holding him close<br>
[ aww lookta the cuteness!]<br>
<br>
