black sweater on with grey skin-tight slacks.  He walked over to her and before he had a chance to speak, she spoke, &quot;Hello Jerron.&quot;  He was suprised as he had not felt any intrusion in his mind.  &quot;I took your name from you friend over there.&quot;  She nodded toward Derek.  Jerron sent out his own thoughts, to inspect this woman who intrigued him.  Before he had a chance to finish, she punched him.  He doubled over in pain.  She winked, &quot;Only way to stop someones mind.  My names Laurana, Lor.  Wanna dance?&quot;  Jerron disliked dancing as it distracted the mind, but he felt compelled to do so her.  She led him onto the floor before he had a chance to respond.  Whether because she knew his answer, or she wouldn't take no as one Jerron wasn't sure.  Admists a crowd of ravers jumping to the music, Jerron and Lor danced slowly.  She rested her head upon her shoulder as they slowly revolved.  A raver jumped into the pair, knocking Lor to the ground.  He appologized and went to help her up, but she didn't care.  Using her mind, she grabbed his heart.  He grabbed his chest as it seared in pain.  A minute went by before he slumped to the ground.  Whether he was dead or merely knocked out Jerron was uncertain.  Lor stood back up, and again rested her head upon his shoulder.  They clasped hands and he put his hand around her waist.  She had a smile upon her face, as if what she had just done was nothing.  &quot;Having fun?&quot;<br>
OOC (If anyone just reading wants, they can take over for Lor.  Otherwise, I'll just get rid of her *grins wickedly*) <p>Ignis Summa Pugnabat, The fires shall cleanse the world.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ubellonakali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bellona Kali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Child of Hate</span><br>  Posts: 194<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/02 7:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/Reineva.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: S'just Life.</span><hr size=1> (sorry i haven't been around! Was at my sister's for three days <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  but i'm back!)<br>
